snippet.title: Hell Let Loose Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the front line at https://www.HellLetLoose.com

Fight across the most brutal battlefields of World War 2 in this epic, team-oriented realistic first person shooter. 

Hell Let Loose is developed by Black Matter in Unreal Engine 4 and will be released for PC on Steam in 2018.

Follow us for all the latest news: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HellLetLoose/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Hell_Let_Loose

Music: “Abaddon” by Brian Armor

Cinematic: David Williams
Motion Designer: Chris Angelius
Sound Mix: Michael Newton
